{"tid":1979450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金剛無預警下被火辣台妹狠飛","createTime":"2020-04-19T12:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:16:15.000Z","uid":46356,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b247cad1fdf8cf816f8a81f97a5a373f12a8b060","tid":1979450,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/TLCVJTFGKRUBC67OINBV44GVFM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FTLCVJTFGKRUBC67OINBV44GVFM%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=dc930905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FTLCVJTFGKRUBC67OINBV44GVFM%2F&h=6ac5792b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/TLCVJTFGKRUBC67OINBV44GVFM/</a><br />\n<br />\n【拍拖1周年】金剛無預警下被火辣台妹狠飛 分手即刪合照：R.I.P<br />\n<br />\n39歲金剛昨晚突然在IG放了一張黑白照，留言：「R.I.P」，惹來網民猜測金剛與擁34D火辣身材的29歲前台灣「國光女神」Nana（梁云菲）分手！台灣《蘋果新聞網》今日向金剛的經理人了解，經理人證實已分手：「二人是和平分手，彼此祝福。」據了解金剛是昨晚無預警下「被分手」，心情既錯愕又難過。本月初二人才放片上視頻平台齊齊做網紅，第一波便一齊去暢泳、潛水，至於分手後還會一起主持網路節目嗎？經理人表示該節目原本就是彈性錄影，目前還沒規劃到下集。<br />\n<br />\n梁云菲亦上載自拍照，似有弦外之音發附文謂：「當你眼淚忍不住要流出來的時候，睜大眼睛，千萬別眨眼。你會看到世界由清晰變模糊的全過程，然後在淚水落下的那一刻一切變得清澈。以前很多人都說當眼淚要掉下來的時候，就倒立吧。但是我不會倒立，那就待在海裏吧。」<br />\n<br />\n金剛和梁云菲在去年4月不約而同地在IG上放閃，貼出「情侶視角」照片，事後二人證實交往，常在IG大方曬恩愛。前天他們才一起主持網路節目，當時金剛接受台灣《蘋果新聞網》訪問時還透露考慮兩年內完成登記結婚，不料隔兩天就傳出情變，令人遺憾。據了解二人交往期間，金剛把梁云菲當小公主般呵護，梁云菲曾透露在一起時自己從來沒洗過頭，顯見金剛對她用情至深，沒想到一過熱戀期，二人開始有爭吵，愛好自由的梁云菲漸漸覺得金剛管她管太多，二人多次溝通，金剛也都配合女方想法給予更多空間，結果正在和朋友度假的梁云菲昨晚突然提出分手，讓金剛措手不及，還在沉澱情傷的金剛更不想看到梁云菲在IG和其他男性朋友及女生朋友一班人開心度假照片，才黯然取消追蹤，並極速刪掉大部份與Nana昔日的恩愛合照。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200419/large/1587273236_c226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587273236_c226.jpg&h=c9a084f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金剛疑是「被分手」，心情難以平伏，深宵在社交網留言：「R.I.P.」。 （IG圖片）"},{"pid":"f186035b4b09e40a0511c94a83b8086519c8b41c","tid":1979450,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"金剛棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5f05eb1a235365a1d801c791f2d8e4f7f5fdf4","tid":1979450,"uid":107681,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"條女個樣真係麻麻...."},{"pid":"d5cfb4c6f2492858ffd161b6068815b77e7e5f54","tid":1979450,"uid":97,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"搞咁多野 金剛帶埋條女上節目比位佢上都飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85df9e7a57aea8f0e9eb6648ae60b9f9366388d3","tid":1979450,"uid":31098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"機會嚟喇，娟姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27da359daffed7b4010ab95a50513cc375753c32","tid":1979450,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"條女正撚到"},{"pid":"1ba26e425f601e0eec4c1c2b1a2781c9f110f8c2","tid":1979450,"uid":97,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85df9e7a57aea8f0e9eb6648ae60b9f9366388d3","tid":1979450,"uid":31098,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"機會嚟喇，娟姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class